OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with largely clear skies
OL,7,Fand evening sunshine to start but
OL,8,Fturning cloudier. Dry and mostly
OL,9,Fcloudy overnight with some clear
OL,10,Fintervals.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FDry with sunny spells for
OL,13,Fmost, but the odd afternoon shower
OL,14,Fpossible. The best of the sunshine in
OL,15,Fthe west with the east cloudier.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
